is very closely connected

00:25:39.380 --> 00:25:41.100
to organizational behavior is

00:25:41.100 --> 00:25:42.220
managerial science.

00:25:42.640 --> 00:25:44.820
What you see on the slide.

00:25:47.240 --> 00:25:48.440
Again, what the management sciences

00:25:48.440 --> 00:25:52.040
are concerned with is the field of management.

00:25:52.040 --> 00:25:54.440
Naturally, we've talked to you about

00:25:54.440 --> 00:25:56.780
this many times before, but as far

00:25:56.780 --> 00:25:58.860
as management is concerned, there

00:25:58.860 --> 00:26:01.540
are also several disciplines that

00:26:01.860 --> 00:26:04.060
approach management from different

00:26:04.060 --> 00:26:05.140
perspectives.

00:26:05.740 --> 00:26:07.780
And naturally, each of these

00:26:07.780 --> 00:26:09.620
perspectives has its own impact,

00:26:09.620 --> 00:26:11.500
its own impact on organizational

00:26:11.500 --> 00:26:13.680
behavior.

00:26:14.460 --> 00:26:15.480
First of all, of course, is management

00:26:15.640 --> 00:26:17.520
itself, the general science

00:26:17.520 --> 00:26:18.760
of management.

00:26:18.760 --> 00:26:21.080
What management styles exist in an

00:26:21.080 --> 00:26:21.960
organization?

00:26:22.640 --> 00:26:23.980
How does delegation of authority,

00:26:23.980 --> 00:26:26.940
delegation of responsibility take place?

00:26:27.720 --> 00:26:30.360
Who takes responsibility for the

00:26:30.360 --> 00:26:32.020
decision being made?

00:26:32.200 --> 00:26:33.920
Who takes responsibility for implementing

00:26:33.920 --> 00:26:35.560
those decisions?

00:26:36.860 --> 00:26:39.360
What is the degree of freedom, this

00:26:39.360 --> 00:26:41.780
is the backlash that the employee

00:26:41.780 --> 00:26:44.240
has in the degree of solving his problems?

00:26:44.740 --> 00:26:46.180
How can he be subordinate?

00:26:48.420 --> 00:26:49.940
What co-subordination exists.

00:26:50.580 --> 00:26:52.320
These are all things that are addressed

00:26:52.320 --> 00:26:54.220
in management courses, and what

00:26:54.220 --> 00:26:55.660
you and I will look at further

00:26:55.660 --> 00:26:56.800
in our course.

00:26:57.240 --> 00:26:59.580
The next discipline that plays

00:26:59.580 --> 00:27:03.440
an important, even in a sense,

00:27:03.440 --> 00:27:05.240
also a determining influence

00:27:05.240 --> 00:27:06.640
on organizational behavior

00:27:06.640 --> 00:27:08.760
is, of course, marketing.

00:27:09.640 --> 00:27:11.440
The study and analysis of the market.

00:27:11.840 --> 00:27:14.020
For all those market laws that

00:27:14.100 --> 00:27:15.880
are known in marketing are naturally

00:27:15.880 --> 00:27:16.660
at work in organizational

00:27:16.660 --> 00:27:17.560
behavior.

00:27:18.160 --> 00:27:19.920
This market is not an abstraction.

00:27:20.080 --> 00:27:23.580
The market is the action of the people

00:27:23.580 --> 00:27:25.780
who are on this market, the action

00:27:25.780 --> 00:27:27.460
of an organization which has

00:27:27.460 --> 00:27:28.320
either a different or a different

00:27:28.320 --> 00:27:28.620
market.

00:27:29.180 --> 00:27:30.900
All those laws on the promotion

00:27:30.900 --> 00:27:34.000
of goods, services which are known in

00:27:34.000 --> 00:27:35.420
marketing, they naturally find

00:27:35.420 --> 00:27:36.720
their manifestation and realization

00:27:36.720 --> 00:27:39.640
in organizational behavior.

00:27:39.840 --> 00:27:41.620
For it is precisely those people

00:27:41.620 --> 00:27:43.820
when they are in the organization,

00:27:43.820 --> 00:27:45.700
They also function, according to

00:27:45.700 --> 00:27:46.800
these or those laws.

00:27:48.220 --> 00:27:50.540
And the organization either achieves

00:27:50.540 --> 00:27:52.880
certain heights on the market,

00:27:53.560 --> 00:27:56.340
develops new niches, displaces competitors,

00:27:56.340 --> 00:27:59.820
produces new products, or,

00:27:59.820 --> 00:28:01.900
as they say, the organization

00:28:02.000 --> 00:28:04.280
gradually comes to naught, the

00:28:04.280 --> 00:28:06.020
death of the organization

00:28:06.020 --> 00:28:07.820
occurs, its disbanding, absorption,

00:28:07.900 --> 00:28:09.600
and another organization with

00:28:09.600 --> 00:28:11.520
new laws of organizational

00:28:11.520 --> 00:28:13.380
behavior, with new ethics,

00:28:13.380 --> 00:28:15.060
with a new culture, new regularities,

00:28:15.180 --> 00:28:17.040
new opportunities emerges.

00:28:17.640 --> 00:28:20.120
The organization, again, does not exist

00:28:20.120 --> 00:28:20.860
in a vacuum.

00:28:20.980 --> 00:28:22.740
Well this is what I have already talked about,

00:28:22.740 --> 00:28:24.260
which again, I want to draw your attention to.

00:28:24.460 --> 00:28:25.880
An organization always exists

00:28:25.880 --> 00:28:27.860
alongside other organizations.

00:28:28.440 --> 00:28:29.700
People who are in one organization

00:28:29.700 --> 00:28:30.800
act and function together

00:28:30.800 --> 00:28:32.380
with people who are in

00:28:32.520 --> 00:28:34.180
other organizations.

00:28:34.600 --> 00:28:36.820
And this, too, is organizational behavior.

00:28:37.160 --> 00:28:38.820
And here, too, are those marketing

00:28:38.820 --> 00:28:40.340
regularities that need to be considered

00:28:40.340 --> 00:28:41.840
and taken into account.

00:28:43.620 --> 00:28:46.080
We have talked mostly about management

00:28:46.080 --> 00:28:48.240
and marketing, about these sciences

00:28:48.240 --> 00:28:49.760
of management.

00:28:50.240 --> 00:28:52.720
But I constantly emphasize, I constantly

00:28:52.780 --> 00:28:53.700
speak about the fact that the

00:28:53.700 --> 00:28:55.000
organization is people.

00:28:55.360 --> 00:28:57.980
So people are the staff of the organization.

00:28:58.340 --> 00:29:00.040
In this regard, when we talk about

00:29:00.040 --> 00:29:01.600
organizational behavior or when

00:29:01.600 --> 00:29:02.780
we talk about organization, of

00:29:03.160 --> 00:29:04.360
course, it's imperative

00:29:04.360 --> 00:29:06.220
to talk about a discipline

00:29:06.220 --> 00:29:08.980
like human resource management.

00:29:09.260 --> 00:29:11.280
What human resource management

00:29:11.280 --> 00:29:13.580
is about, it covers the whole range

00:29:13.580 --> 00:29:15.460
of issues related to human

00:29:15.460 --> 00:29:17.180
performance in an organization.

00:29:17.960 --> 00:29:19.080
Personnel selection.

00:29:20.620 --> 00:29:23.280
If a person, some organization starts

00:29:23.280 --> 00:29:25.760
to work, he was found, he turned

00:29:25.760 --> 00:29:27.620
out to meet the requirements,

00:29:27.620 --> 00:29:29.700
those competencies that

00:29:29.780 --> 00:29:30.760
are required for the

00:29:30.760 --> 00:29:32.180
position he occupies.

00:29:32.660 --> 00:29:33.780
And consequently, the person

00:29:33.780 --> 00:29:35.660
was employed by that organization,

00:29:35.860 --> 00:29:37.560
and then he begins to function

00:29:37.560 --> 00:29:38.900
in that organization.

00:29:38.900 --> 00:29:40.520
He begins to behave in

00:29:40.520 --> 00:29:42.660
this organization in a certain way.

00:29:43.120 --> 00:29:45.520
He behaves according to the requirements

00:29:45.640 --> 00:29:46.780
that are imposed on him.

00:29:47.940 --> 00:29:49.980
Behave in accordance with the function

00:29:50.060 --> 00:29:51.600
that functions and operates.

00:29:52.400 --> 00:29:54.640
And, accordingly, the selection

00:29:54.640 --> 00:29:56.720
of personnel is the first

00:29:56.820 --> 00:30:01.460
task that arises here for any

00:30:01.460 --> 00:30:03.340
person who begins to work somewhere.

00:30:04.280 --> 00:30:05.840
A person works in an organization, and

00:30:05.840 --> 00:30:07.360
here, of course, you have to pay attention

00:30:07.360 --> 00:30:09.140
as a training and development

00:30:09.140 --> 00:30:13.100
of the person who is in the organization.

00:30:13.300 --> 00:30:14.600
If you're good at something,

00:30:14.600 --> 00:30:16.180
if you're a successful manager,

00:30:16.180 --> 00:30:17.300
then naturally the organization

00:30:17.360 --> 00:30:18.800
is interested in improving,

00:30:18.940 --> 00:30:21.120
developing, focusing

00:30:21.960 --> 00:30:23.820
those skills that are useful

00:30:23.820 --> 00:30:25.700
to you, adding those skills

00:30:25.880 --> 00:30:26.740
that you lack.

00:30:27.740 --> 00:30:33.120
Building a career ladder, a

00:30:33.680 --> 00:30:35.160
career learning structure are

00:30:35.160 --> 00:30:37.240
all things that hunt too to this area.

00:30:38.220 --> 00:30:39.860
In addition to developmental training, the

00:30:39.860 --> 00:30:41.980
same organization will be in the business

00:30:41.980 --> 00:30:45.320
of evaluating and motivating the person as an employee.

00:30:47.020 --> 00:30:48.860
You can be put in the talent pool,

00:30:48.860 --> 00:30:52.760
you can depend on that assessment,

00:30:52.760 --> 00:30:55.880
on the evaluations that you get

00:30:56.040 --> 00:30:56.900
in the organization, in

00:30:56.900 --> 00:30:58.300
terms of solving certain tasks,

00:30:58.300 --> 00:31:00.380
in terms of the assessments,

00:31:00.380 --> 00:31:04.080
it determines that level of achievement,

00:31:04.080 --> 00:31:05.920
that level of development that

00:31:06.060 --> 00:31:07.320
you're going to have in

00:31:07.320 --> 00:31:09.420
that particular organization.

00:31:10.260 --> 00:31:11.600
That's the whole area that

00:31:11.600 --> 00:31:13.580
goes into human resource management.

00:31:13.980 --> 00:31:16.880
Well at the end of the day, we don't usually

00:31:16.880 --> 00:31:18.880
talk about it, but it's the same personnel

00:31:18.880 --> 00:31:20.420
business of production.

00:31:20.600 --> 00:31:22.640
Sick days, vacations, business trips,

00:31:22.780 --> 00:31:24.540
this is all organizational behavior, too.

00:31:24.980 --> 00:31:25.980
Modern organizations

00:31:25.980 --> 00:31:28.160
are quite mobile and mobile.

00:31:28.740 --> 00:31:31.540
And a person can be sent on a business

00:31:31.540 --> 00:31:35.300
trip, a person can fall ill.

00:31:35.520 --> 00:31:37.160
All this, again, requires those

00:31:37.760 --> 00:31:39.320
or other documentary forms.

00:31:39.740 --> 00:31:41.300
And then, each of us, coming

00:31:41.300 --> 00:31:43.940
to work, presents a

00:31:43.940 --> 00:31:44.860
resume.

00:31:45.000 --> 00:31:46.900
A resume is in a certain way

00:31:46.900 --> 00:31:50.800
somehow confirmed your labor,

00:31:50.800 --> 00:31:52.700
personnel successes that

00:31:52.700 --> 00:31:53.220
you had.

00:31:53.620 --> 00:31:55.100
This is all something that belongs to the field

00:31:55.100 --> 00:31:56.280
of human resources management.

00:31:56.880 --> 00:31:58.900
And when we talk about aggressive behavior,

00:31:58.900 --> 00:32:00.680
then personnel management

00:32:00.680 --> 00:32:03.060
is, perhaps, to the greatest extent

00:32:03.060 --> 00:32:04.500
with all of its regularities,

00:32:04.500 --> 00:32:06.180
with all of its possibilities,

00:32:06.180 --> 00:32:09.140
incorporated into this organizational

00:32:09.140 --> 00:32:10.480
behavior.

00:32:11.100 --> 00:32:14.580
Very often there is even a dispute

00:32:14.580 --> 00:32:17.820
between specialists in HR and specialists

00:32:17.820 --> 00:32:18.860
in organizational behavior,

00:32:18.860 --> 00:32:21.260
that in fact the HR-function

00:32:21.260 --> 00:32:23.660
is the same organizational

00:32:23.660 --> 00:32:25.200
behavior, and therefore one more

00:32:25.200 --> 00:32:27.380
discipline does not make sense.

00:32:27.800 --> 00:32:30.220
But due to the fact that we have

00:32:30.220 --> 00:32:32.040
already talked about the links

00:32:32.040 --> 00:32:33.940
of organizational behavior with various

00:32:33.940 --> 00:32:35.320
social disciplines, we can still

00:32:35.320 --> 00:32:38.680
see that these very links, which

00:32:38.680 --> 00:32:40.580
arise with a large complex of psychological,

00:32:40.580 --> 00:32:41.640
managerial, sociological,

00:32:41.640 --> 00:32:43.480
organizational problems, testify

00:32:43.580 --> 00:32:45.340
to the fact that organizational

00:32:45.340 --> 00:32:46.820
behavior in its tasks,

00:32:46.820 --> 00:32:49.620
goals and solved problems

00:32:49.740 --> 00:32:51.780
is much broader

00:32:51.780 --> 00:32:54.700
than personnel management.

00:32:54.700 --> 00:32:55.860
Moreover, we can even say that

00:32:56.040 --> 00:32:58.380
the field of HR, it is largely

00:32:58.380 --> 00:33:01.360
included in organizational

00:33:01.360 --> 00:33:02.680
behavior.

00:33:05.660 --> 00:33:08.500
In modern management, there

00:33:08.500 --> 00:33:10.600
is such a concept as organization

00:33:10.600 --> 00:33:11.600
theory.

00:33:12.080 --> 00:33:13.540
After all, the same organizations come

00:33:13.540 --> 00:33:14.480
in different forms.

00:33:14.840 --> 00:33:15.880
An industrial organization,

00:33:16.000 --> 00:33:17.360
a service organization, organizations

00:33:17.480 --> 00:33:21.540
that are related to the performance

00:33:21.540 --> 00:33:23.220
of certain functions.

00:33:23.720 --> 00:33:25.760
There are different types of organizations.

00:33:28.000 --> 00:33:30.400
And naturally, each of these organizations,

00:33:30.400 --> 00:33:32.680
if it has a different type, a different

00:33:32.680 --> 00:33:34.860
scope, has its own organizational

00:33:35.060 --> 00:33:36.940
behavior, its own goals,

00:33:36.940 --> 00:33:39.640
its own tasks, its own approaches.

00:33:39.740 --> 00:33:40.540


00:33:41.280 --> 00:33:43.340
And of course if we want to understand,

00:33:43.340 --> 00:33:44.740
to analyze the organizational

00:33:44.740 --> 00:33:46.120
behavior that emerges in this

00:33:46.220 --> 00:33:47.660
or that sphere, it is essential for

00:33:48.040 --> 00:33:50.120
us to understand what kind

00:33:50.120 --> 00:33:51.720
of organization a person

00:33:51.720 --> 00:33:53.480
is in, what kind of organizations

00:33:53.480 --> 00:33:54.900
we are talking about.

00:33:54.900 --> 00:33:56.400
Again I draw your attention, it makes

00:33:56.680 --> 00:33:57.760
no sense to talk about organizations

00:33:57.760 --> 00:34:01.080
in general, about the market in general.

00:34:02.120 --> 00:34:03.680
Organizational behavior is a

00:34:03.680 --> 00:34:05.680
significant specific discipline.

00:34:05.960 --> 00:34:08.800
It deals with the analysis of the behavior

00:34:08.800 --> 00:34:11.920
of concrete living people in this or

00:34:11.920 --> 00:34:13.020
that organization.

00:34:13.340 --> 00:34:15.820
It applies the general scientific

00:34:15.820 --> 00:34:19.240
laws that have been discovered in

00:34:19.240 --> 00:34:21.940
this or that field to the analysis

00:34:21.940 --> 00:34:23.280
of human actions in the

00:34:23.280 --> 00:34:24.840
organization where he is.

00:34:27.240 --> 00:34:28.980
Again, there are many managerial

00:34:28.980 --> 00:34:31.620
sciences, and we talked about management,

00:34:31.620 --> 00:34:33.060
marketing, personnel management,

00:34:33.160 --> 00:34:34.620
organization theory, just

00:34:34.620 --> 00:34:37.320
as in the analysis of the social

00:34:37.320 --> 00:34:40.660
branch, these are far from

00:34:40.660 --> 00:34:42.520
all sciences, but traditionally

00:34:42.520 --> 00:34:44.060
it so happened that organizational

00:34:44.060 --> 00:34:45.580
behavior is largely

00:34:45.580 --> 00:34:47.220
based on them.

00:34:48.400 --> 00:34:50.620
The only other thing that is important

00:34:50.620 --> 00:34:52.360
to mention, and to which one should pay

00:34:53.040 --> 00:34:57.800
attention, is the area of innovation

00:34:57.800 --> 00:35:00.620
management, which is currently developing

00:35:00.620 --> 00:35:03.300
very strongly and successfully.

00:35:03.840 --> 00:35:05.020
Naturally, as far as innovations

00:35:05.020 --> 00:35:08.280
are concerned, they came to us

00:35:08.280 --> 00:35:11.180
from the Western tradition, because,

00:35:11.240 --> 00:35:12.300
after all, business there is

00:35:12.300 --> 00:35:15.560
much more actively developed and

00:35:15.560 --> 00:35:16.600
on much higher quality

00:35:16.600 --> 00:35:18.880
aspects than in Russia, and

00:35:18.880 --> 00:35:20.120
I think there is nothing surprising

00:35:20.120 --> 00:35:20.960
in that.

00:35:21.920 --> 00:35:23.600
So, as for the Western

00:35:23.600 --> 00:35:26.620
management, they paid attention

00:35:26.620 --> 00:35:30.500
to the fact that a great number

00:35:30.500 --> 00:35:31.700
of modern organizations,

00:35:31.700 --> 00:35:35.460
huge investments are

00:35:35.460 --> 00:35:37.320
made in innovations.

00:35:38.020 --> 00:35:40.000
It is significantly connected with the

00:35:40.000 --> 00:35:42.560
development of information structures, with

00:35:42.960 --> 00:35:45.380
the development of computer structures,

00:35:45.860 --> 00:35:47.200
with the development of virtual

00:35:47.200 --> 00:35:48.300
organizations, which we will

00:35:48.300 --> 00:35:49.780
talk about later.

00:35:50.900 --> 00:35:52.480
So innovations, they just imply

00:35:52.480 --> 00:35:57.200
the process of constant changes.

00:35:57.660 --> 00:35:59.780
It used to be that there was an organization,

00:35:59.780 --> 00:36:01.400
you came to this organization,

00:36:01.400 --> 00:36:03.280
you worked in it until you retired,

00:36:03.280 --> 00:36:06.080
and nothing changed.

00:36:07.320 --> 00:36:11.900
That was characteristic of

00:36:11.960 --> 00:36:14.080
the 1960s, 1970s, even 1980s,

00:36:14.080 --> 00:36:17.220
when there were quite certain

00:36:17.220 --> 00:36:20.400
norms and attitudes in organizations

00:36:20.400 --> 00:36:22.020
that practically

00:36:22.020 --> 00:36:23.280
didn't change.

00:36:23.380 --> 00:36:25.380
People were changing, but the

00:36:25.380 --> 00:36:26.780
functions were the same.

00:36:27.120 --> 00:36:29.080
Today we live in an era of

00:36:29.080 --> 00:36:30.380
constant change.

00:36:30.740 --> 00:36:33.460
New commercial areas are emerging,

00:36:33.460 --> 00:36:36.020
new areas of business are emerging.

00:36:36.960 --> 00:36:39.180
And, accordingly, a different

00:36:39.180 --> 00:36:40.800
number of innovations are constantly

00:36:40.800 --> 00:36:42.640
being introduced, which must

00:36:42.640 --> 00:36:45.880
be applied if you want to defend

00:36:45.880 --> 00:36:48.160
your market niche, at least, or

00:36:48.160 --> 00:36:49.920
expand that niche accordingly.

00:36:51.040 --> 00:36:53.340
It is in this connection that different

00:36:53.340 --> 00:36:55.640
innovative enterprises and venture

00:36:55.640 --> 00:36:57.240
companies are being developed

00:36:57.640 --> 00:36:58.700
more and more.

00:36:59.400 --> 00:37:01.580
Today no one can say which

00:37:02.000 --> 00:37:04.340
sphere, which part of the

00:37:04.340 --> 00:37:06.180
market will largely prevail

00:37:06.180 --> 00:37:07.080
tomorrow.

00:37:07.120 --> 00:37:10.880
Analysts are fighting over it, but

00:37:10.880 --> 00:37:12.720
if everything were that simple,

00:37:12.720 --> 00:37:14.180
we would not be witnesses

00:37:14.180 --> 00:37:16.560
of constant innovations, which arise.

