01:03:56.480 --> 01:03:59.460
his children, he will be interested

01:03:59.500 --> 01:04:01.960
in working better and producing

01:04:01.960 --> 01:04:02.840
more.

01:04:03.320 --> 01:04:04.800
In this way, the problem

01:04:04.800 --> 01:04:06.400
of restrictionism, which confronted

01:04:06.400 --> 01:04:09.520
industry in the late 19th century,

01:04:09.760 --> 01:04:11.220
which had been battled over

01:04:11.220 --> 01:04:14.460
in various ways, was solved scientifically.

01:04:14.460 --> 01:04:15.040


