were introduced, then indeed

01:04:27.300 --> 01:04:29.080
the phenomenon of restrictionism

01:04:29.080 --> 01:04:31.360
gradually began to come

01:04:31.360 --> 01:04:31.900
down.

01:04:31.900 --> 01:04:32.880
Well of course, within certain limits,

01:04:32.880 --> 01:04:34.900
but nevertheless this problem was

01:04:34.900 --> 01:04:36.540
also deprived by Taylor.

01:04:38.640 --> 01:04:41.100
Again, Taylor had followers,

01:04:41.100 --> 01:04:42.060
there were predecessors,

01:04:42.060 --> 01:04:45.060
but here are the results that

01:04:45.060 --> 01:04:47.940
were obtained at this time, they

01:04:47.940 --> 01:04:50.920
led to the creation of the

01:04:50.920 --> 01:04:53.360
classical model of organization,

01:04:53.360 --> 01:04:54.960
and accordingly the classical

01:04:54.960 --> 01:04:56.020
model of organizational

01:04:56.020 --> 01:04:58.040
behavior, which was developed

01:04:58.660 --> 01:05:02.340
and created by Henri

01:05:02.340 --> 01:05:03.780
Fayle.

01:05:05.260 --> 01:05:06.960
Again, of course, it was not only

01:05:06.960 --> 01:05:10.020
Fayele who had a hand in this,

01:05:10.020 --> 01:05:12.020
but in his works it was well structured,

01:05:12.020 --> 01:05:13.780
and accordingly, the classical

01:05:14.020 --> 01:05:15.500
model of organization,

01:05:15.500 --> 01:05:16.580
it correlates with

01:05:16.580 --> 01:05:17.920
Henri Fayele.

01:05:18.480 --> 01:05:20.360
As far as Fayele and as far as the classical

01:05:20.360 --> 01:05:21.760
model is concerned, there are

01:05:21.760 --> 01:05:24.060
four principled approaches that

01:05:24.060 --> 01:05:26.280
have characterized organizational

01:05:26.280 --> 01:05:28.620
behavior in the late 19th,

01:05:28.620 --> 01:05:31.220
early 20th century.

01:05:32.240 --> 01:05:33.880
First of all, the first

01:05:33.880 --> 01:05:35.320
point is that there was a rigid

01:05:35.320 --> 01:05:37.360
division of labor.

01:05:38.820 --> 01:05:40.240
The worker worked on the same

01:05:40.240 --> 01:05:42.880
machine, the work on the same machine.

01:05:43.040 --> 01:05:44.960
Some workers handled parts,

01:05:45.060 --> 01:05:47.500
others handled them, others

01:05:47.500 --> 01:05:50.040
did other work, and still

01:05:50.120 --> 01:05:51.940
others carried parts.

01:05:53.320 --> 01:05:55.980
But the main thing here was that there was

01:05:55.980 --> 01:05:57.080
a narrow specialization.

01:05:57.320 --> 01:05:58.860
Everyone had to do a certain

01:05:58.860 --> 01:06:01.200
part, a certain element

01:06:01.200 --> 01:06:02.160
in the work.

01:06:02.320 --> 01:06:03.640
To a large extent this was precisely

01:06:03.640 --> 01:06:07.000
what came into play under the influence

01:06:07.000 --> 01:06:08.440
of Taylor's scientific organization

01:06:08.440 --> 01:06:09.260
of labor.

01:06:10.720 --> 01:06:12.660
The second important element

01:06:12.660 --> 01:06:14.640
of the classical model is that there

01:06:14.880 --> 01:06:17.440
are certain commands and

01:06:17.440 --> 01:06:20.540
orders that are passed from the

01:06:20.540 --> 01:06:22.100
top down, and only from the

01:06:22.100 --> 01:06:22.860
top down.

01:06:23.300 --> 01:06:26.200
There is a supervisor who knows what

01:06:26.200 --> 01:06:28.000
you have to do, how you have to do

01:06:28.000 --> 01:06:29.180
it, when you have to do it.

01:06:30.680 --> 01:06:32.840
If you succeed, if you fail, that's

01:06:33.160 --> 01:06:34.620
your problem.

01:06:34.800 --> 01:06:36.240
You have to fulfill those prescriptions,

01:06:36.240 --> 01:06:38.680
you have to fulfill those functions

01:06:38.680 --> 01:06:40.180
that are assigned to you,

01:06:40.180 --> 01:06:42.860
that are passed down to you.

01:06:42.860 --> 01:06:47.900
In this connection, the third point of

01:06:47.900 --> 01:06:49.760
the classical model, the one-man rule,

01:06:49.760 --> 01:06:53.560
the existence of a single commander,

01:06:53.560 --> 01:06:55.340
was very important.

01:06:56.680 --> 01:06:58.700
This consensus was called

01:06:58.700 --> 01:06:59.880
one boss.

01:07:00.900 --> 01:07:02.580
The simple fact is that

01:07:02.580 --> 01:07:04.600
if more than one boss

01:07:04.600 --> 01:07:06.060
