01:11:15.760 --> 01:11:18.500
of organizational behavior, which

01:11:18.500 --> 01:11:19.960
had been introduced, which had

01:11:20.220 --> 01:11:22.160
been substantiated, which

01:11:22.160 --> 01:11:23.760
had been cradled by Taylor,

01:11:23.760 --> 01:11:26.880
by Fayol, by other authorities,

01:11:27.360 --> 01:11:31.880
needed at least a modification.

01:11:31.880 --> 01:11:33.240


01:11:34.700 --> 01:11:35.960
And, as always,

01:11:38.480 --> 01:11:41.700
a significant contributor to

01:11:41.700 --> 01:11:45.080
this modification was, again, the

01:11:45.640 --> 01:11:48.660
scientific experiments that were conducted

01:11:48.660 --> 01:11:52.660
in the late '20s, respectively, formally

01:11:53.600 --> 01:11:55.320
they lasted from 1927 to 1932,

01:11:55.320 --> 01:11:58.040
these experiments that were

01:11:58.040 --> 01:11:59.460
conducted in the town

01:11:59.460 --> 01:12:02.640
of Hawthorne at the Western

01:12:02.640 --> 01:12:04.740
Digital plant.

01:12:06.260 --> 01:12:09.460
Usually these experiments, now

01:12:09.460 --> 01:12:11.320
called the Hawthorne experiments,

01:12:11.320 --> 01:12:12.600
are associated with

01:12:13.620 --> 01:12:16.140
the name of Elton Mayo.

01:12:16.460 --> 01:12:18.820
But in fact, a whole group

01:12:18.820 --> 01:12:20.680
of authors were involved in this

01:12:20.680 --> 01:12:21.780
experiment.

01:12:22.120 --> 01:12:24.760
Which included Fries, Rettlisberger,

01:12:26.280 --> 01:12:28.460
Elton Mayo, William, Dixon, and others.

01:12:30.620 --> 01:12:32.680
When these experiments were

01:12:32.680 --> 01:12:34.860
carried out, the main idea

01:12:34.900 --> 01:12:36.740
that came out of them was that

01:12:36.880 --> 01:12:40.340
in addition to these objective characteristics,

01:12:40.340 --> 01:12:42.240
which must be taken into account,

01:12:43.000 --> 01:12:44.700
which are considered in the

01:12:44.800 --> 01:12:45.880
classical model, it is necessary

01:12:45.880 --> 01:12:47.940
to take into account informal

01:12:47.940 --> 01:12:50.420
