01:12:56.160 --> 01:12:57.760
of the classical period, of the

01:12:57.760 --> 01:12:59.400
Taylor period, it was still

01:12:59.400 --> 01:13:01.500
formal organizational behavior,

01:13:01.500 --> 01:13:03.880
it was necessary to identify

01:13:03.880 --> 01:13:06.420
