01:13:06.540 --> 01:13:09.140
exist, that hierarchy of

01:13:09.140 --> 01:13:10.900
relationships that exist.

01:13:10.900 --> 01:13:14.440
That hierarchy of commands, that function

01:13:14.440 --> 01:13:16.480
of authority that exists, and you

01:13:16.480 --> 01:13:18.140
