01:13:44.680 --> 01:13:46.980
drawn attention to this, but

01:13:46.980 --> 01:13:49.000
Taylor just didn't emphasize it.

01:13:49.340 --> 01:13:50.940
The main thing for Taylor, after all, was

01:13:50.940 --> 01:13:54.320
to formalize this or that relationship.

01:13:57.580 --> 01:14:00.260
That's right, up to the 1920s,

01:14:00.260 --> 01:14:04.460
up to the 20-30s this is the

01:14:04.460 --> 01:14:05.840
classical Fayol model that

01:14:05.840 --> 01:14:08.200
